1
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,760
And Fei, let me tell you.

2
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,760
Gang is very loyal.

3
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,480
He's the best ore washer in Dayang Village.

4
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,539
We don't need to discuss that, right?

5
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:18,580
And the price he gave me this time,

6
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,920
is just this much.

7
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:33,160
So Fei, I was thinking,

8
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,560
your price,

9
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,240
could be a bit lower too?

10
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,520
Mr. Xiao,

11
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,330
you're the boss.

12
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,000
It's up to you.

13
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,400
Come on.

14
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,600
I am the boss,

15
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,000
but I've always been democratic.

16
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,800
Everyone knows that, right?

17
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:03,120
So it's settled then, okay?

18
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,520
I have things to do.

19
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,320
I've got to go.

20
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,720
Don't be so uptight.

21
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,880
I'm off.

22
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,760
Hey, wait.

23
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,720
Liao Fei.

24
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:34,480
Yang Gang, what do you mean?

25
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,440
Calm down.

26
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,760
I can't calm down!

27
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,040
Believe it or not, I could kill you right now.

28
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,700
It's all Xiao Tianman's plot.

29
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,200
Xiao Tianman's plot.

30
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,079
Your family is in trouble.

31
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,320
I can help you.

32
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,680
But have you thought about it?

33
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,720
Don't I have a family?

34
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,320
Don't their families need to survive?

35
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,160
Listen to me.

36
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:51,420
I never thought about undercutting you.

37
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,960
I never thought about it.

38
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,200
I'll figure something out, okay?

39
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,200
I'll find a way.

40
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,480
I only earn enough for my mother's medical bills.

41
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,360
I'll give you the rest of what I earn, okay?

42
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,920
Let's do as you say.

43
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,450
Get back to work.

44
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:53,720
What is it?

45
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,320
Gold. It's gold.

46
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,320
For real?

47
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,280
It's gold.

48
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,960
We're washing sand from Mine K26.

49
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:14,920
That means Mine K26 has a gold vein.

50
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,560
I'm sure of it.

51
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:20,120
We found a gold vein.

52
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,720
Mr. Xiao.

53
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,520
Now every mine entrance is guarded by security.

54
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:30,850
Situ Hongtang wants to cut off our income.

55
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,800
Lao Er.

56
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:42,680
Can't you handle a few security guards?

57
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,360
Understood, Mr. Xiao.

58
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,280
I'm on it.

59
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,159
Come back.

60
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,280
Don't kill anyone.

61
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,860
Don't leave any evidence.

62
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,660
Don't worry, Mr. Xiao.

63
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,080
Gang, come take a look.

64
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,680
What's wrong?

65
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:55,960
It's gold ore.

66
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,560
It's gold ore.

67
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,560
Really.

68
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,140
You three in front!

69
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,920
What are you holding?

70
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,520
Who are you?

71
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,560
- Run!
- Stop!

72
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,960
After them!

73
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:24,680
Stop!

74
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:28,640
Go, go.

75
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,120
Stop!

76
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,320
Stop right there!

77
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,200
Don't run!

78
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,720
You three.

79
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:54,180
Did you see three guys in security uniforms?

80
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,320
Why should I tell you?

81
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:01,800
What are you doing here so late?

82
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:06,810
A villager from Dayang Village taking a leak on Dayang Village's land.

83
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,440
Jing, they work for Liao Fei.

84
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,940
We probably won't catch anyone tonight.

85
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,650
Security squad, listen up.

86
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,160
All security personnel,

87
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:23,480
return to the dorms for roll call.

88
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,560
Alright, it's over.

89
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,600
Damn it.

90
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,120
Du Jing is doing a head count.

91
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,720
What's the rush?

92
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,600
Can you outrun a motorcycle?

93
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,760
Hold on tight. Brother Fei is taking you for a ride.

94
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,680
Security squad, fall in!

95
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,760
Yang Gang, Yang Gaoyong, Luo Zhengqiang.

96
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:32,179
Where are Yang Gang, Yang Gaoyong, and Luo Zhengqiang?

97
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,120
Yang Gang! Yang Gaoyong! Luo Zhengqiang!

98
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:39,039
Here! Here! Here!

99
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,320
Forgot! Forgot! Forgot!

100
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,120
Didn't hear you! Didn't hear you!

101
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,960
Forgot! Forgot! Forgot!

102
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,620
Why didn't you say something?

103
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:50,930
Drinking on the job?

104
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:52,960
Want some?

105
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,200
I'm docking your pay.

106
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,280
Dock it, then.

107
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,320
About last night,

108
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,360
thanks.

109
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,560
No big deal.

110
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,800
You know, we're both from Dayang Village.

111
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,160
We've actually known each other a long time, right?

112
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,690
But we've never been close.

113
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,880
I've always known you are a

114
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,360
generous,

115
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,320
manly,

116
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,050
and good person.

117
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,920
- Me?
- Yeah.

118
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,760
A good person.

119
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,570
Who'd believe that?

120
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:46,960
Let me ask you something.

121
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,320
I'm curious.

122
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:50,330
Tell me, why would someone like you

123
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:54,880
work for a dog like Xiao Tianman?

124
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,240
No.

125
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,840
You aren't working for Xiao Tianman.

126
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,840
I'm doing it for my mom's illness.

127
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,440
I'm just trying to make money.

128
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,280
I'm just making money, too.

129
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,920
My brother is sick as well.

130
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,720
Then we're the same.

131
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,080
Exactly the same.

132
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,200
Cheers.

133
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,000
What's wrong with you today?

134
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,600
You seem distracted.

135
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:49,600
Xiaomei.

136
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,010
Have you been happy lately?

137
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:55,360
Yes, I have.

138
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,480
Do I look unhappy?

139
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,000
No.

140
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,810
I'm happy whenever you're around.

141
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,330
As long as you're happy.

142
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:11,600
What is actually wrong?

143
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,440
What's up with you today?

144
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,080
Talk to me.

145
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,520
I'm always here.

146
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,360
I'm with you.

147
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,320
You're getting sweeter by the day.

148
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,560
What can you do?

149
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:44,290
Do you remember Section Chief Sun?

150
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,000
I remember.

151
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,180
The corrupt official.

152
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,970
Right, that corrupt official.

153
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:54,600
The factory actually does a lot of business with him.

154
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:57,440
A huge part of our profit comes from him.

155
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:00,760
But now,

156
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,520
he doesn't want to work with me anymore.

157
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:07,240
I'm afraid I can't keep this going.

158
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,760
Then... how can I help?
